text: You know you’ve been #shopping too much when you get a @FedEx email that something will be delivered by the end of day #Friday and you have no idea what it could be...
@CarrieBurling Hello Carrie, this is Julie. May I assist you today?Please DM your full name, address, city, state, zip code, tracking number, phone number, and email address. https://t.co/7vnSkvqx3r
@FedExHelp Hi Julie! Thanks for the tweet, but I figured out what is being shipped! Getting Xmas shopping done early for a change and couldn’t remember what this shipment was for lol
@CarrieBurling Good for you Carrie. Have a good rest of your day.
